thin if BB fer sure.  Finds tha dwarf.  Nae druids or rangers tha means trackin . or ifin it ok then all has ta be rangers und such.  there be some er nice places ta sit high up or tha nicks und folds O tha earth.  Cou be hard ta find even with trackin.  Wou have ta do a trial run ta see how it be. <BR> <BR>Me keeps thinkin O things.  A race about caludrin startin und endin at unrest has a few kin in places ta make sure they go by. it a circle O a zone. <BR> <BR>Just some ideas ta ponder on. <!-/Text-!> <P> 
